eal closed in july  investmentsedit nova scotia power emera maine emera caribbean light and power holdings  lucelec barbados light and power company grand bahama power company emera energy bear swamp bayside power brooklyn power emera utility services emera new brunswick maritimes and northeast pipeline emera newfoundland and labrador openhydro group ltd atlantic hydrogen inc algonquin power  utilities teco energy referencesedit  tampa bay times tampa electric announces its sale to canadian company emera september    emera  our investments httpwwwemeracomenhomeourbusinesscorporatestructuredefaultaspx retrieved august    emera  news release details httpwwwemeracomenhomemediacentrearchivedpressreleasesnewsreleasedetailsaspxsourceparamsreqid retrieved august    algonquin power  utilities corp external linksedit official site v t e sptsx  companies of canada february   agnico eagle mines agrium arc resources bank of montreal barrick gold bce inc blackberry bombardier brookfield asset management cameco canadian imperial bank of commerce canadian national canadian natural resources canadian pacific canadian tire ccl industries cenovus energy cgi group constellation software couchetard crescent point energy dollarama emera enbridge encana first quantum minerals franconevada fortis inc gildan goldcorp husky energy imperial oil inter pipeline kinross gold loblaw companies magna international manulife financial metro national bank of canada pembina pipeline potashcorp power corporation restaurant brands international rogers communications royal bank of canada saputo scotiabank shaw communications silver wheaton snclavalin sun life financial suncor energy teck telus thomson reuters torontodominion bank transcanada valeant weston waste connections retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleemeraoldid categories sptsx  indexsptsx composite indexemeracompanies listed on the toronto stock exchangepower companies of canadacompanies based in halifax nova scotianatural gas pipel